snippet: A federal judge in Austin prevented Texas from enforcing a rule that would have banned Planned Parenthood from participating in a health care program for low-income women.
abstract: Judge Lee Yeakel, a federal judge in Austin, Tex, issues decision that will prevent Texas from enforcing a rule that would have banned Planned Parenthood clinics statewide from participating in a health care program for low-income women.
lead_paragraph: A federal judge in Austin prevented Texas from enforcing a rule that would have banned Planned Parenthood from participating in a health care program for low-income women.

headline.main: Texas: Judge Prevents Ban on Funds to Planned Parenthood
headline.print_headline: Texas: Judge Prevents Ban On Funds To Planned Parenthood
